metadata.name: Meka Rhinos #1
metadata.description:
MekaRhinos is a special collection on the ethereum network with a limited number of 3.333 unique pieces. Thanks to the specially developed staking system, MekaRhino holders will generate daily $RHNO tokens and will be able to mint the upcoming Mutant MekaRhino collection using $RHNO tokens.

MekaRhino holders will also able to use $RHNO tokens to purchase limited edition items available in the Merch Shop.
